cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.NE, cs.CL 

This paper is focused on improving the interpretability of deep learning models, specifically convolution neural networks. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.CV (Computer Vision). The paper also mentions logical networks and cognitive learning, which suggests a possible connection to sub-categories cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) and cs.CL (Computation and Language).
